Oxfam Website Content Summary

Period between 2019-05-29 and 2019-06-02.

Qualified Page Views:
For immersive stories a qualified page view is counted if any of the following happen:
1) a user spends 45 or more seconds on a page and scrolls through at least 50% of the page
2) a user spends 45 or more seconds on a page and views at least 50% of any audio or video elements on the page or
3) a user clicks a CTA.

For non-immersive stories a qualified page view is counted if any of the following happen:
1) a user spends 30 or more seconds on a page and scrolls through at least 50% of the page
2) a user spends 30 or more seconds on a page and views at least 50% of any audio or video elements on the page or
3) a user clicks a CTA.

Dataset Summary Statistics

This is a summary of the content-level data in this report.
For example, the average number of unique page views for a given piece of content in this dataset was: 8.
The 3rd Quartile (3rd Qu.) for unique page views of content in this dataset was 3. This means that 75% of the content in this data set had less than or equal to 3 unique page views.
The most number of unique page views any given content had was 366. The least number of unique page views any given content had was 1.
